{"tid":167910,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"三月尾一日東京賞櫻","createTime":"2017-03-23T07:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T02:01:06.000Z","uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92a01964d939bb47d5922afb4562dc3041c81dae","tid":167910,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"其實出過post問過<br />\n可能唔夠資料搜集所以無人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊有一日係東京<br />\n應該係櫻花全開個幾日黎<br />\n<br />\n目前對中目黑同千鳥之淵好有興趣<br />\n如果想一個睇日櫻一個夜櫻<br />\n應該點排好？"},{"pid":"a2115d2d86e471896cecf685ed5d81bc8a194f76","tid":167910,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7496b1e9c2ee66f11406298c14780216b807cac8","tid":167910,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab5b2d0b4f551374d91281959eed207ac66ccb6","tid":167910,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e79e8c1172021cc18855680941d36e23047d9b","tid":167910,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"日頭千鳥，夜晚中目黑<br />\n不過千鳥未必夠你睇成日，可以搭多個新宿御苑係中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb6c078a30642776e9d64d8a00838aa5489c1b8","tid":167910,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日頭千鳥，夜晚中目黑<br />\n不過千鳥未必夠你睇成日，可以搭多個新宿御苑係中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚御苑好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打仲有無去過東京其他位睇櫻花？"},{"pid":"7f2884e69bc8ed714eecf72fa7f8211ce5bb35e5","tid":167910,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日頭千鳥，夜晚中目黑<br />\n不過千鳥未必夠你睇成日，可以搭多個新宿御苑係中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚御苑好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打仲有無去過東京其他位睇櫻花？</blockquote><br />\n其實我都係月尾第一次去，不過做過下資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上野公園，六義園都會去"}]}